commitResults.messageTitle: Level-1: David Chatbot can echo the commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types command bye.
Level-2: add a list to store texts entered by the user, display them back when requested
Level 3: add the ability to mark tasks as done, and add the ability to change the status back to not done.

Level 4: create task types: to do, deadline, event to do: tasks without any date/time attached deadline: tasks that need to be done before a specific date/time event: tasks that start at a specific date/time and ends at a specific date/time
